darkbox - A Fast and Portable Console IO Server
ptnio - Portable TCP Network IO

Repository structure :
    - bin : Darkbox binaries (Windows binaries are built using the given tcc)
    - lib : Some libraries used in some darkbox projects.
    - darkbox : Darkbox server source code.
    - darkbox_i : Darkbox Standalone Input module
    - makemenu : Darkbox Menu module (WIP)
    - ptnio : ptnio source code
    - tcc : Customised Tiny C Compiler for Windows
    - tests : Some tests for darkbox and misc
    - extras : Some other stuff.

Useful links :
 - Dos9 Project : dos9.org
 - TheBATeam website : thebateam.org
 - dostips forum : dostips.com/forum/viewforum.php?f=3
